#------------------------------
# Files Description
#------------------------------
.
|-- README
|-- mrlite.py               # Mapreduce-Lite scheduler
|-- mrlite_options.py       # scheduler command line options parser
|-- mrlite_options_test.py  # unittest for options parser
|-- worker.py               # script to run map worker or reduce worker
|-- util.py                 # common utility



#------------------------------
# Usage of Mapreduce-Lite scheduler
#------------------------------

1. Read comments at the head of "mrlite.py"
2. Read help of "mrlite.py" by running "./mrlite.py -h"
3. Read documentation of Mapreduce-Lite at "http://paralgo.oa.com/mrlite.xml"
